---
import LocaleLayout from '../../layouts/LocaleLayout.astro';
import Button from '../../components/ui/Button.astro';
---

<LocaleLayout
  title="Contact"
  description="Discutons de votre projet. Premier échange de 30 minutes, sans engagement."
>
  <section class="py-[var(--space-section)]">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[var(--space-container-narrow)] px-[var(--space-gutter)]">
      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-[length:var(--text-h1)] font-semibold text-ink mb-4">
          Discutons
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-mist max-w-lg mx-auto">
          Un projet en tête ? Une question ? Prenons 30 minutes pour en parler.
          Sans engagement, sans pitch commercial.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Contact options -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
        <!-- Calendly -->
        <a
          href="https://calendly.com/christophevanengelen"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-cloud hover:border-accent/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all"
        >
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-accent-subtle text-accent flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">
            Réserver un créneau
          </h2>
          <p class="text-mist text-sm mb-4">
            30 minutes pour faire connaissance et comprendre vos enjeux.
          </p>
          <span class="text-accent text-sm font-medium inline-flex items-center gap-2 group-hover:gap-3 transition-all">
            Voir les disponibilités
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" />
            </svg>
          </span>
        </a>

        <!-- Email -->
        <a
          href="mailto:cve@hi-def.be"
          class="group bg-white rounded-xl p-8 border border-cloud hover:border-accent/30 hover:shadow-md transition-all"
        >
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-accent-subtle text-accent flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors">
            M'envoyer un email
          </h2>
          <p class="text-mist text-sm mb-4">
            Je réponds sous 48h, souvent plus vite.
          </p>
          <span class="text-accent text-sm font-medium">
            cve@hi-def.be
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Social links -->
      <div class="bg-cloud rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-sm text-mist mb-4">
          Vous pouvez aussi me retrouver sur
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-6">
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/christophevanengelen/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-slate hover:text-accent transition-colors"
          >
            <span class="sr-only">LinkedIn</span>
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://github.com/Christophevanengelen/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-slate hover:text-accent transition-colors"
          >
            <span class="sr-only">GitHub</span>
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M12 .297c-6.63 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.303 3.438 9.8 8.205 11.385.6.113.82-.258.82-.577 0-.285-.01-1.04-.015-2.04-3.338.724-4.042-1.61-4.042-1.61C4.422 18.07 3.633 17.7 3.633 17.7c-1.087-.744.084-.729.084-.729 1.205.084 1.838 1.236 1.838 1.236 1.07 1.835 2.809 1.305 3.495.998.108-.776.417-1.305.76-1.605-2.665-.3-5.466-1.332-5.466-5.93 0-1.31.465-2.38 1.235-3.22-.135-.303-.54-1.523.105-3.176 0 0 1.005-.322 3.3 1.23.96-.267 1.98-.399 3-.405 1.02.006 2.04.138 3 .405 2.28-1.552 3.285-1.23 3.285-1.23.645 1.653.24 2.873.12 3.176.765.84 1.23 1.91 1.23 3.22 0 4.61-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.92.42.36.81 1.096.81 2.22 0 1.606-.015 2.896-.015 3.286 0 .315.21.69.825.57C20.565 22.092 24 17.592 24 12.297c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a
            href="https://x.com/van_christophe"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="text-slate hover:text-accent transition-colors"
          >
            <span class="sr-only">X</span>
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- FAQ -->
      <div class="mt-16">
        <h2 class="text-[length:var(--text-h3)] font-semibold text-ink mb-8 text-center">
          Questions fréquentes
        </h2>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <details class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-cloud group">
            <summary class="px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer font-medium text-ink flex justify-between items-center">
              Quels sont vos tarifs ?
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-mist group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-mist">
              <p>
                Je travaille au forfait ou en régie selon les projets. Les tarifs dépendent de la complexité,
                de la durée, et du niveau d'engagement. Discutons de votre besoin pour établir un devis adapté.
              </p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-cloud group">
            <summary class="px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer font-medium text-ink flex justify-between items-center">
              Êtes-vous disponible actuellement ?
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-mist group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-mist">
              <p>
                Ma disponibilité varie selon les projets en cours. Le meilleur moyen de savoir :
                réservez un créneau et on en discute !
              </p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="bg-white rounded-xl border border-cloud group">
            <summary class="px-6 py-4 cursor-pointer font-medium text-ink flex justify-between items-center">
              Travaillez-vous en remote ?
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-mist group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
              </svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-4 text-mist">
              <p>
                Oui, je travaille principalement en remote. Je peux me déplacer pour des workshops,
                des séminaires, ou des phases intensives si nécessaire.
              </p>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</LocaleLayout>
